| Stripe | Payments | Implemented |
| A/B Testing (PostHog/Vercel) | Experiments | Not implemented |
| Live Chat (Intercom/Crisp) | Support | Not implemented |

### API Changes Required

| Endpoint | Change | Priority |
|----------|--------|----------|
| `GET /credits` | Add `trialDaysRemaining` field | High |

### Database Changes

**None required** - Trial info available via Stripe API (`subscription.trial_end`)

### Risk Assessment

